{"id":43701,"date":"2024-01-20T09:03:00","date_gmt":"2024-01-20T03:33:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=43701"},"modified":"2024-02-09T18:51:30","modified_gmt":"2024-02-09T13:21:30","slug":"7-exposed-brick-wall-decor-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/7-exposed-brick-wall-decor-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Stunning Exposed Brick Wall Decor Ideas for An Envious Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Seven<strong> <\/strong>exposed brick wall decor ideas for your home<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Beauty lies in the eyes of the beholder. Perhaps that\u2019s why exposed brick interior has been called timeless style, a quirky feature, and sometimes even an eyesore. But, despite all this, this type of interior design has never failed to charm most homeowners.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Exposed brick decor is an art piece in itself. It is perfect for minimalism lovers. It does perfectly with Scandinavian, cottage, industrial, urban loft, and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/vintage-living-room\/\">vintage home interiors<\/a>. Most of the time, it does not require additional adornment. However, here are our brick wall decor ideas to make it more striking.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">White Brick Wall Decorating Tips For Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The naturally exposed brick wall may seem too rustic to some people. A white brick wall is a perfect alternative. It adds a softness to the space. In the image below, we have used a customised multipurpose TV unit with an attached study desk and bookshelf. The light wooden laminate of the unit creates a bright contrast hue. We have wall-mounted the TV and added two floating shelves for additional storage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Designer Tip:<\/strong> If you are on a tight budget, achieve this same look with adhesive wall stickers. It\u2019s a great renter-friendly option.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092555\/white-brick-wall-decor-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"White brick wall decor ideas\" class=\"wp-image-43708\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092555\/white-brick-wall-decor-for-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092555\/white-brick-wall-decor-for-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092555\/white-brick-wall-decor-for-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092555\/white-brick-wall-decor-for-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">White brick wall decor for a soft and bright living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Half-n-Half Black Decorative Brick Wall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The combination of black brick walls and wooden panels is magical for this home. The contrast of colours makes the living room aesthetically alluring. Coupled with that, the bright yellow floating TV unit with drawers is a great option to hide the messy items you wouldn\u2019t want in plain sight. If this half-n-half style of exposed brick wall decor appeals to you, talk to one of our designers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092549\/half-n-half-black-brick-wall-decor.jpg\" alt=\"Black brick wall decor\" class=\"wp-image-43707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092549\/half-n-half-black-brick-wall-decor.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092549\/half-n-half-black-brick-wall-decor-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092549\/half-n-half-black-brick-wall-decor-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092549\/half-n-half-black-brick-wall-decor-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Multiply the allure of your home with black brick wall decor<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Study Zone by the Brick Wall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In the era of accent walls, the exposed brick wall is the quickest way to create one for your home. We have chosen red brick wall decor for this makeshift study\/work zone in this apartment. Minimal accessories give an industrial-style vibe to the place. A black metal study desk and three-layer wall shelves in a similar style complement the other elements. It provides the room with a very edgy look. We have also placed a modular bookcase with hidden storage. Four seamless drawers are on the bottom to keep items organised and tidy. We have also placed a potted plant for the much-needed pop of colour.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092543\/study-zone-by-the-brick-wall.jpg\" alt=\"Brick wall decor that have a study zone\" class=\"wp-image-43706\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092543\/study-zone-by-the-brick-wall.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092543\/study-zone-by-the-brick-wall-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092543\/study-zone-by-the-brick-wall-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092543\/study-zone-by-the-brick-wall-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Red brick wall decor for study room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Decorative Brick Wall Tiles For Bathroom Designing<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bathroom-design\/\">bathroom design<\/a>, the use of white brick-pattern wall tiles is not something new. But you can play with these decorative brick wall tiles in many ways to make something phenomenal. Take a cue from the bathroom shown in the image. It\u2019s the definition of luxury bathrooms. We have used a combination of traditional white wall tiles and decorative half-moon-shaped tile chips with midnight blue paint, which gives this bathroom an otherworldly vibe. The patterned floor tiles in similar colours complete the whole look. Try this at your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092537\/decorative-brick-wall-tiles-for-bathroom-designing.jpg\" alt=\"Decorative brick wall tiles for bathroom designing\" class=\"wp-image-43705\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092537\/decorative-brick-wall-tiles-for-bathroom-designing.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092537\/decorative-brick-wall-tiles-for-bathroom-designing-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092537\/decorative-brick-wall-tiles-for-bathroom-designing-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092537\/decorative-brick-wall-tiles-for-bathroom-designing-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Mesmerising bathroom decor with decorative brick wall tiles<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Moody Brick Wall Bedroom Decor<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Take inspiration from this dark, moody bedroom. With just a portion of the exposed brick wall cemented, the bedroom gives away a mysterious, rugged vibe. It is primarily because of the dark four-poster wooden bed. If you want to incorporate this style, consider decorating it with a few mixed-sized picture frames, decorative string lights, and small metal furniture. You can also swap glossy ceramic planters with concrete ones to match the masculine vibe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092531\/moody-brick-wall-bedroom-decor.jpg\" alt=\"Exposed brick wall bedroom decor\" class=\"wp-image-43704\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092531\/moody-brick-wall-bedroom-decor.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092531\/moody-brick-wall-bedroom-decor-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092531\/moody-brick-wall-bedroom-decor-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092531\/moody-brick-wall-bedroom-decor-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Dark, masculine brick wall bedroom decor<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Stunning Outdoor Brick Wall Decor<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Rarely you might have seen exposed brick walls on the balcony. Take inspiration from the image- looks phenomenal, doesn&#8217;t it? We decorated the space by handling a metal open shelf and a round-shaped wooden shelf. We created a comfy seating space on the modular, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/space-saving-shoe-rack-ideas\/\">multipurpose shoe cabinet<\/a>. We completed the look of this exquisite balcony with some green plants and knick-knacks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092524\/stunning-outdoor-brick-wall-decor.jpg\" alt=\"Outdoor brick wall decor\" class=\"wp-image-43703\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092524\/stunning-outdoor-brick-wall-decor.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092524\/stunning-outdoor-brick-wall-decor-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092524\/stunning-outdoor-brick-wall-decor-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092524\/stunning-outdoor-brick-wall-decor-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Balcony\/backyard brick wall decor\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Personalied home interiors for all tastes and budget\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/27115725\/personalied-home-interiors-for-all-tastes-and-budget-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Colourful Brick Wall Home Decor<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who said a brick wall only has to be red? Paint them green as we did in the image below and quickly transform the space without breaking the bank. You can decorate it with your favourite picture frames and create a gallery wall. The combination of white furniture and walls in contrast with the sage green brick wall looks fabulous.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092519\/colourful-brick-wall-home-decor.jpg\" alt=\"Colourful brick wall decor\" class=\"wp-image-43702\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092519\/colourful-brick-wall-home-decor.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092519\/colourful-brick-wall-home-decor-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092519\/colourful-brick-wall-home-decor-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/23092519\/colourful-brick-wall-home-decor-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Paint your exposed brick walls to add cheerfulness to your bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>How did you like these designs? Are they lovely? If you, too, want to have an exposed brick wall decorated in your home and give it an instant upgrade, reach out to our designers today. Check out our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/\">blog section<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">design gallery<\/a> for more such design ideas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/brick-wall-design-ideas\/\">Brick Wall Bedroom Designs for an Instant Upgrade<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <s